gram\": \"withdrawals\", \"from\": 162, \"to\": 173}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Immediately after the match, Ebdenannounced that he had officially retired from singles tennisand turned his attention to the men's doubles draw with John Peers.\", \"from\": 219, \"to\": 380, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 369, \"end\": 379, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Peers\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"John Peers\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Peers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Peers\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the match\", \"from\": 237, \"to\": 246}, {\"ngram\": \"singles tennisand\", \"from\": 299, \"to\": 316}, {\"ngram\": \"his attention\", \"from\": 324, \"to\": 337}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's doubles\", \"from\": 341, \"to\": 358}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Seven days later, the Aussies won an Olympic gold medal, coming from a set and break down to beat Austin Krajicek and Rajeev Ram of the USA in a match tiebreak 6-7(6) 7-6(1) [10-8].\", \"from\": 382, \"to\": 563, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 480, \"end\": 495, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Austin_Krajicek\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Austin Krajicek\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Austin_Krajicek\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Austin_Krajicek\"}, {\"begin\": 500, \"end\": 510, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rajeev_Ram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rajeev Ram\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rajeev_Ram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rajeev_Ram\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Aussies\", \"from\": 400, \"to\": 411}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic gold medal\", \"from\": 416, \"to\": 437}, {\"ngram\": \"a set\", \"from\": 451, \"to\": 456}, {\"ngram\": \"the USA\", \"from\": 514, \"to\": 521}, {\"ngram\": \"a match tiebreak\", \"from\": 525, \"to\": 541}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ebden looked lost on the court when he came out to face top seed Djokovic in singles last Saturday.\", \"from\": 565, \"to\": 664, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ebden\", \"from\": 565, \"to\": 570}, {\"ngram\": \"the court\", \"from\": 586, \"to\": 595}, {\"ngram\": \"top seed\", \"from\": 621, \"to\": 629}, {\"ngram\": \"Djokovic\", \"from\": 630, \"to\": 638}, {\"ngram\": \"singles\", \"from\": 642, \"to\": 649}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It took 46 minutes for him to win his first and only game of the match after training 0-6 0-4.\", \"from\": 665, \"to\": 759, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"46 minutes\", \"from\": 673, \"to\": 683}, {\"ngram\": \"his first and only game\", \"from\": 699, \"to\": 722}, {\"ngram\": \"the match\", \"from\": 726, \"to\": 735}, {\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 742, \"to\": 750}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Early in the second set,he even resorted to trying to quit the match, jokingly handing his racket to a spectator so he could sub out.\", \"from\": 760, \"to\": 893, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the second set\", \"from\": 769, \"to\": 783}, {\"ngram\": \"the match\", \"from\": 819, \"to\": 828}, {\"ngram\": \"his racket\", \"from\": 847, \"to\": 857}, {\"ngram\": \"a spectator\", \"from\": 861, \"to\": 872}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 36-year-old had not played a singles match in almost two years, since an outing in the qualifying rounds of the ATP 250 event in Winston-Salem.\", \"from\": 895, \"to\": 1042, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1028, \"end\": 1041, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Winston-Salem_Open\", \"score\": 0.9999980145545734, \"rank\": 1.985427683386114e-06, \"text\": \"Winston-Salem\", \"types\": [\"Q500834\", \"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Winston-Salem_Open\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Winston-Salem_Open\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a singles match\", \"from\": 926, \"to\": 941}, {\"ngram\": \"almost two years\", \"from\": 945, \"to\": 961}, {\"ngram\": \"an outing\", \"from\": 969, \"to\": 978}, {\"ngram\": \"the qualifying rounds\", \"from\": 982, \"to\": 1003}, {\"ngram\": \"the ATP 250 event\", \"from\": 1007, \"to\": 1024}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And he officially quit the game afterwards.\", \"from\": 1043, \"to\": 1086, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the game\", \"from\": 1066, \"to\": 1074}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Safe to say I am officially retired from singles after that,\\\" he wrote onInstagram.\", \"from\": 1087, \"to\": 1171, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"singles\", \"from\": 1129, \"to\": 1136}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After turning his attention back to his real specialism, doubles, he managed to win his first gold medal alongside compatriot and neighbour Peers.\", \"from\": 1173, \"to\": 1319, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his attention\", \"from\": 1187, \"to\": 1200}, {\"ngram\": \"his real specialism\", \"from\": 1209, \"to\": 1228}, {\"ngram\": \"his first gold medal\", \"from\": 1257, \"to\": 1277}, {\"ngram\": \"compatriot and neighbour Peers\", \"from\": 1288, \"to\": 1318}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After securing the win, Ebden confessed that his loss to Djokovic was on his mind. \\\"\", \"from\": 1320, \"to\": 1404, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1377, \"end\": 1385, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.907967326476901e-26, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the win\", \"from\": 1335, \"to\": 1342}, {\"ngram\": \"Ebden\", \"from\": 1344, \"to\": 1349}, {\"ngram\": \"his loss\", \"from\": 1365, \"to\": 1373}, {\"ngram\": \