"to\": 2166}, {\"ngram\": \"the chance\", \"from\": 2191, \"to\": 2201}, {\"ngram\": \"his singles career\", \"from\": 2224, \"to\": 2242}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He continued: \\\"I did come off that singles match fully focused on the doubles.\", \"from\": 2244, \"to\": 2322, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the doubles\", \"from\": 2310, \"to\": 2321}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Literally when I got the call up to play [singles], Lleyton was like, 'No do not play, you save your body, make sure do not get injured.\", \"from\": 2323, \"to\": 2459, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the call\", \"from\": 2344, \"to\": 2352}, {\"ngram\": \"singles\", \"from\": 2365, \"to\": 2372}, {\"ngram\": \"Lleyton\", \"from\": 2375, \"to\": 2382}, {\"ngram\": \"your body\", \"from\": 2419, \"to\": 2428}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You are not here for that, I want a medal in the doubles or the mixed, whatever.'\", \"from\": 2460, \"to\": 2541, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 2494, \"to\": 2501}, {\"ngram\": \"the doubles\", \"from\": 2505, \"to\": 2516}, {\"ngram\": \"the mixed, whatever\", \"from\": 2520, \"to\": 2539}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And I said, 'Okay, I will play but I promise I will not get injured.'\", \"from\": 2543, \"to\": 2613, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So my main goal that match was just not to get injured and I did that, had a hit, had some fun.\", \"from\": 2614, \"to\": 2709, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my main goal\", \"from\": 2617, \"to\": 2629}, {\"ngram\": \"a hit\", \"from\": 2689, \"to\": 2694}, {\"ngram\": \"some fun\", \"from\": 2700, \"to\": 2708}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Got to officially retire from singles which was nice.\", \"from\": 2710, \"to\": 2763, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"singles\", \"from\": 2740, \"to\": 2747}]}, {\"sentence\": \"My wife was liking that, I never officially played my last official retirement si